We Can't Dance  
  
  *This is a classic rock tune and I couldn't believe no one had tabbed it*  
  *(although it is pretty simple)... This is by no means entirely correct,*  
  *as the original has a synthesizer that adds a good bit of the punch,*  
  *and the bass does a lot too.*  
